chart.name: Top Commands/sec
chart.programText: A = data('mysql_commands.*', filter=filter('plugin', 'mysql')).sum(by=['sf_metric']).top(count=5).publish(label='A')

chart.name: Top Commands/sec
chart.programText: A = data('mysql_commands.*', filter=filter('plugin', 'mysql') and filter('host', 'integration-test-mysql-5.6-0')).mean(by=['sf_metric']).top(count=5).publish(label='A')

chart.name: Total Query Cache Operations/sec, Size
chart.programText:
A = data('cache_result.qcache-inserts', filter=filter('plugin', 'mysql')).sum().publish(label='A')
B = data('cache_result.qcache-prunes', filter=filter('plugin', 'mysql')).sum().publish(label='B')
C = data('cache_size.qcache', filter=filter('plugin', 'mysql')).sum().publish(label='C')

chart.name: Mutations/sec
chart.programText:
A = data('mysql_commands.insert', filter=filter('plugin', 'mysql')).sum().publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('mysql_commands.update*', filter=filter('plugin', 'mysql')).sum(by=['sf_metric']).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = data('mysql_commands.delete', filter=filter('plugin', 'mysql')).sum().publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (A+B+C).publish(label='D', enable=False)
E = (D).min().publish(label='E')
F = (D).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='F')
G = (D).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='G')
H = (D).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='H')
I = (D).max().publish(label='I')

chart.name: Selects/sec
chart.programText: A = data('mysql_commands.select', filter=filter('plugin', 'mysql') and filter('host', 'integration-test-mysql-5.6-0')).publish(label='A')

chart.name: Overall Query Cache Hit %
chart.programText:
A = data('cache_result.qcache-hits', filter=filter('plugin', 'mysql')).sum().publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('cache_result.qcache-not_cached', filter=filter('plugin', 'mysql')).sum().publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/(A+B)).publish(label='C')

chart.name: Inserts, Updates, Deletes /sec

C = data('mysql_commands.delete', filter=filter('host', 'integration-test-mysql-5.6-0') and filter('plugin', 'mysql')).publish(label='C')

chart.name: Top Mutations/sec
chart.programText:
A = data('mysql_commands.insert', filter=filter('plugin', 'mysql')).mean(by=['host']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('mysql_commands.update*', filter=filter('plugin', 'mysql')).mean(by=['host', 'sf_metric']).publish(label='B', enable=False)

chart.name: Selects/sec 24h Change %
chart.programText:
A = data('mysql_commands.select', filter=filter('plugin', 'mysql') and filter('host', 'integration-test-mysql-5.6-0')).mean(over='1h').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).timeshift('1d').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/B - 1).scale(100).publish(label='C')
